<h3>Optimize for Gemini (and Google AI Overviews)</h3>
<p>Since Gemini pulls from Google's index, traditional SEO is your entry point.</p>
<ul>
<li>Rank in Google's top 20 for your target queries</li>
<li>Implement <a href="/blog/schema-markup-for-blog-posts/">FAQ and Article schema markup</a></li>
<li>Write clear, structured answers in your content headers</li>
<li>Keep content fresh (update within 6 months)</li>
