<li>Build brand authority across multiple platforms</li>
<li>Allow <a href="/blog/ai-crawlers-guide/">AI crawlers</a> (GPTBot) in your <code>robots.txt</code></li>
<li>Create an <a href="/blog/llms-txt-guide/">llms.txt file</a> for AI-readable site structure</li>
<li>Publish original data and research that AI cannot find elsewhere</li>
<li>Follow the <a href="/blog/blog-geo-checklist/">GEO optimization checklist</a></li>
</ul>
